Run various services like HTTP servers

Usage:
  llm-proxy run [command]

Available Commands:
  server      Run HTTP server

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for run

Global Flags:
      --log-format string   Log format: text, json (default: text if interactive, json otherwise)
      --log-level string    Log level: debug, info, warn, error (default "info")

Use "llm-proxy run [command] --help" for more information about a command.
